description: They say opposites attract and that's never more true than when you put sweet, rich ice creams and a fine artisan chocolate together with the sharp and wonderful taste of a salted caramel pretzel! The Crave Bar is a locally produced, hand-crafted super premium ice cream bar that sits upon a salted caramel covered pretzel rod!  The perfect way to "Mash-Up" these fantastic flavors including Salted Caramel-Licious, Midnight Vanilla Mash-Up, Milk chocolate Madness, Peanut Butter Bash and Cappuccino Craze... you'll Crave this fantastic ice cream truck!
name: The Crave Bar Flyer
